{"type":"message","id":"44844022","parentId":"87b7abec","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:27:13.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the context monitor cron job is running every 5 minutes. The current status shows:- Context usage: 67% (133,611/200,000 tokens)- This exceeds the 60% warning threshold but is below the 85% auto-switch threshold\n\nThis is just a monitoring cron job. It ran and reported the status. Since we're at 67%, we're above the warning threshold (60%) but below the auto-switch threshold (85%). According to the skill, the auto-switch happens at 85%, not at 60%.\n\nThe job has `delivery.mode: \"none\"`, which means it doesn't deliver any message to the user. This is just an internal monitoring check.\n\nSince this is running in an isolated sub-agent session (as shown by `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"`), I should just acknowledge that the monitor ran and report the status. The user will see this as the result of the cron job.\n\nCurrent status:\n- 67% context usage (133,611 / 200,000 tokens)\n- Above 60% warning threshold ⚠️\n- Below 85% auto-switch threshold ✅\n- No action required yet\n\nThe system is working as designed. I'll just report HEARTBEAT_OK since there's no urgent action needed - we're still below the 85% threshold where automatic session switching would occur.","thinkingSignature":"7ba10c50eb04946c85fa94ce73a04b5b608f22d6c1e9f3cbb3e0ee8dbd2bda5b"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n📊 **Context Monitor 报告**\n\n| 指标 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 当前使用 | 67% (133,611 / 200,000 tokens) |\n| 警告阈值 | 60% ⚠️ 已超过 |\n| 自动切换阈值 | 85% ✅ 尚未达到 |\n| 下次检查 | 5分钟后 |\n\n上下文使用率已超过60%警告阈值，但尚未达到85%自动切换阈值。系统继续正常运行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7221,"output":380,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44603,"cost":{"input":0.0021663,"output":0.00045599999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037323599999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","ti